products.title: Voile Natural Roller Blind
products.description: Their voile range of fabrics create a natural feature of the rooms natural light, and are fantatic at creating some privacy without sacrificing light. This cream natural coloured screen fabric, in its neutral colour and clean finish, creates a centre point of your window. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, which is why this cream blind is not only made by their expert team in the heart of yorkshire, but comes with customer-first service and guarantees.

products.title: Splash Natural Hessian Roller Blind
products.description: Their splash range of fabrics are both beautiful and contemporary. Their roller blinds can be manufactured with either white or chrome control chains which ensures you get the desired finish for your room. Also, as their made to measure blinds come with a 5 year guarantee you can rest assured you are investing in a piece that will stand the test of time. products.title: Meadow Lark Natural Roller Blind
products.description: Light and bright, the meadow lark roller blind is ideal for enhancing a minimalist interior. The grey and white hues of the fabric are simple and versatile and will look sleek and clean at your windows, whilst the pretty wildflower design adds a touch of traditional charm. As well as looking great, this window blind also boasts pollen and dust mite reducing qualities.
